snippet.textDisplay: Hameed bhai....perhaps u r new to this kind of brotherhood among Hindus and Muslims, especially in classical music. Music is like meditation, it takes the person to a different level of consciousness where the realization that the same God is prayed in different forms. Perhaps you don't know that renowned artistes like Amjad Ali Khan start their concerts with Ganesh vandan. By the way, his wife is a Hindu. Actually, it is silly to even discuss about religion. Music itself is a religion.
